   Note:  Prior to tightening the screws on the front panels on a Block 1.8 system, verify the alignment of the cassette through the cassette door by inserting a cassette.

1.  Reinstall the panels and reconnect the cassette door assembly cable.

2.  Return the door to the normal position.  Clean the rear surface of the door with deionized water.

