2.  Connect the cable to output connector of the 4412 Bird Watt Meter.

3.  Connect a test cable from the RF generator to the input end of the 4412 Bird Watt meter.

CAUTION:  Make sure the cable is securely connected so that it does not short across the enclosure.

4.  Set up a Bird Watt meter on the X10 kilowatt scale. The slug arrow should point towards the RF match. Start the Vacuum RF Test in AutoTest. At this point you may continue the entire RF Power Test using the AutoTest Vacuum_RF menu.

