Introduction

This section is about the AutoTest board. The AutoTest Board enables service personnel to perform calibration and product certification procedures more easily.  The procedures featured are those procedures that are benefited by using the AutoTest board.  Some procedures are the same as those used with the Service Test board, others automate manual service test procedures.

AutoTest is menu driven and selections are made from the control panel display LCD by using the function keys on the control panel.  The use of the function keys as displayed on the LCD is as follows:

